<subSubSection id="8C8E6575FFD66A69F8239EDA17D1B2ED" pageId="45" pageNumber="803" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="C42B36FEFFD66A69F8239EDA17D1B2ED" blockId="45.[2014,2609,2099,2527]" pageId="45" pageNumber="803">
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFFD66A69F8239EDA16DCB396" authorityName="Thomas" authorityYear="1915" box="[2015,2268,2179,2212]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Nyctophilus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="45" pageNumber="803" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="sherrini">Nyctophilus sherrini</taxonomicName>
is tentatively in the 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFFD66A69F60E9EDA19F9B3F9" authorityName="Tomes" authorityYear="1858" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Nyctophilus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="45" pageNumber="803" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="gouldi">gouldi</taxonomicName>
group based on some morphological evidence, but this is in need of additional research. 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFFD66A69F7899EA0177FB228" authorityName="Thomas" authorityYear="1915" box="[2165,2431,2297,2330]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Nyctophilus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="45" pageNumber="803" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="sherrini">Nyctophilus sherrini</taxonomicName>
, N. 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFFD66A69F62D9EA01429B228" authorityName="Parnaby" authorityYear="2009" box="[2513,2601,2297,2330]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Nyctophilus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="45" pageNumber="803" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="corbeni">corbeni</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFFD66A69F8239F78164EB270" authorityName="J. E. Gray" authorityYear="1844" box="[2015,2126,2337,2370]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Nyctophilus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="45" pageNumber="803" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="major">N. major</taxonomicName>
, and N. shirleyaewere previously included under 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFFD66A69F7579F11175DB25B" baseAuthorityName="E. Geoffroy" baseAuthorityYear="1806" box="[2219,2397,2376,2409]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Nyctophilus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="45" pageNumber="803" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="timoriensis">N. timoriensis</taxonomicName>
, but they were recently recognized as distinct species, and the name 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFFD66A69F7449FCE173EB28A" baseAuthorityName="E. Geoffroy" baseAuthorityYear="1806" box="[2232,2366,2455,2488]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Nyctophilus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="45" pageNumber="803" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="timoriensis">timoriensis</taxonomicName>
is now regarded as a species inquirenda. Monotypic.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
